DOCUMENT 7 — PROOF & SIGNAL REPOSITORY

Rejoin Media | Knowledge Library

Purpose
To systematically capture, organize, and reuse proof that validates Rejoin Media’s credibility, effectiveness, and worldview.

This document exists to:

Reduce friction in selling

Prevent under-claiming or over-claiming

Ground messaging in reality

Turn lived experience into reusable assets

SECTION 1 — TYPES OF PROOF (REFERENCE)

All proof fits into one or more of the following categories:

Outcome Proof — measurable or observable results

Process Proof — evidence the method works, even mid-journey

Identity Proof — credibility from lived experience

Resonance Proof — “this is me” reactions

Behavioral Proof — actions people take as a result of your work

Not all proof needs to be dramatic. Consistency > magnitude.

